#compdef microbin
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# microbin — secure, configurable file-sharing and URL shortening web app
#             (Rust, 4,381★)
#
# upstream: https://github.com/szabodanika/microbin
# author : Daniel Szabo (szabodanika)
# license: BSD-3-Clause
#
# Source-direct completion: every flag below is verbatim from src/args.rs
# on the szabodanika/microbin tip — clap-derive `Args` struct with
# `#[clap(long, env = "MICROBIN_*", default_value_t)]` attributes parsed
# exactly as declared.  Every flag has a corresponding `MICROBIN_*`
# environment variable for container-friendly configuration.
#
# Direct deps from Cargo.toml (selected):
#   syntect          5.2.0   ← canonical Rust pure-Rust syntax highlighting
#                              library (this axis) — by Tristan Hume
#                              (trishume/syntect); pure-Rust Sublime-Text-
#                              compatible syntax highlighter using the
#                              same `.sublime-syntax` grammar files as
#                              Sublime Text itself.  Powers bat, delta,
#                              presenterm, mdcat, mq, lapce, helix
#                              (via syntect-aware bridge), and most Rust
#                              tools that need pretty-printed code.
#                              microbin uses syntect to syntax-highlight
#                              pasted code snippets in the browser-side
#                              paste view (toggleable via the
#                              `--highlightsyntax` flag).
#   actix-web                (HTTP server)
#   askama                   (Jinja-style templating)
#   rusqlite                 (optional SQLite backend)
#   clap (derive)            (CLI parsing)
#   serde + serde_json
#
# microbin is a single-binary file-sharing + URL-shortening + pastebin
# web app — Docker-friendly, env-var configurable, supports both file
# uploads and text pastas, with optional encryption (client-side via
# WebCrypto + server-side at-rest), QR codes for share URLs, syntax
# highlighting via syntect, basic-auth + uploader passwords + admin
# panel, expiry policies + burn-after-read, and either a SQLite-backed
# DB or a flat JSON DB.  Single binary, ~10MB, runs on Raspberry Pi
# class hardware.
#
# === AXIS 180 OPENER — pure-language syntax highlighting libraries ======
# Axis position: Rust=235 OPENS Axis 180 at slot 1/0/0.  Canonical Rust
# pure-language syntax highlighting library is `syntect` by Tristan
# Hume (trishume/syntect) — reads the same `.sublime-syntax` /
# `.tmTheme` files as Sublime Text and emits HTML / terminal / raw
# token output.  Used by bat (the `cat`-with-syntax-highlighting CLI),
# delta (git diff renderer), presenterm (terminal slide tool), mdcat
# (markdown terminal viewer), mq (markdown query tool), Lapce editor,
# Helix editor (via tree-sitter + syntect bridge), microbin (this
# CLI's pasta syntax highlighting), and effectively every Rust tool
# that pretty-prints source code.
#
# Cycle position in current 3+1 micro-cycle:
#   Rust=235     ← THIS FILE              (axis 180 OPENS, slot 1/0/0)
#   Go=235       ← next round              (axis 180 continues, slot 2/0/0)
#   TS-Node=235  ← round after             (axis 180 CLOSES at triple-235, slot 1/1/1)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

_microbin() {
    _arguments -s -S \
        '(- *)'{-h,--help}'[print help]' \
        '(- *)'{-V,--version}'[print version]' \
        '--auth-basic-username=[HTTP Basic Auth username (env MICROBIN_BASIC_AUTH_USERNAME)]:user:' \
        '--auth-basic-password=[HTTP Basic Auth password (env MICROBIN_BASIC_AUTH_PASSWORD)]:password:' \
        '--auth-admin-username=[admin panel username (default admin, env MICROBIN_ADMIN_USERNAME)]:user:' \
        '--auth-admin-password=[admin panel password (default m1cr0b1n, env MICROBIN_ADMIN_PASSWORD)]:password:' \
        '--editable=[allow editing pastas (default true)]:bool:(true false)' \
        '--footer-text=[custom footer text]:text:' \
        '--hide-footer[hide page footer]' \
        '--hide-header[hide page header]' \
        '--hide-logo[hide microbin logo]' \
        '--no-listing[disable public pasta listing]' \
        '--highlightsyntax=[syntax-highlight code pastas via syntect (default true)]:bool:(true false)' \
        '(-p --port)'{-p,--port=}'[HTTP port (default 8080, env MICROBIN_PORT)]:port:' \
        '(-b --bind)'{-b,--bind=}'[bind address (default 0.0.0.0, env MICROBIN_BIND)]:IP:' \
        '--private=[default pastas to private (default true)]:bool:(true false)' \
        '--pure-html[disable JS-based features (render plain HTML)]' \
        '--json-db[use flat JSON database instead of SQLite]' \
        '--public-path=[public URL path prefix]:path:' \
        '--short-path=[URL shortening path prefix]:path:' \
        '--uploader-password=[require password for uploads]:password:' \
        '--readonly[run in read-only mode (no writes)]' \
        '--show-read-stats=[show read-counter stats (default true)]:bool:(true false)' \
        '--title=[custom site title]:title:' \
        '(-t --threads)'{-t,--threads=}'[worker thread count (default 1)]:N:' \
        '(-g --gc-days)'{-g,--gc-days=}'[garbage-collect pastas older than N days (default 90)]:days:' \
        '--enable-burn-after=[enable burn-after-N-reads feature (default true)]:bool:(true false)' \
        '(-d --default-burn-after)'{-d,--default-burn-after=}'[default burn-after-N-reads value (default 0 = disabled)]:N:' \
        '--wide[wide layout]' \
        '--qr[show QR code for share URL]' \
        '--eternal-pasta[enable eternal-pasta option]' \
        '--enable-readonly=[allow read-only pastas (default true)]:bool:(true false)' \
        '--default-expiry=[default pasta expiry (default 24hour)]:expiry:(never 1min 10min 1hour 24hour 1week 1month 1year)' \
        '--max-expiry=[maximum allowed expiry (default 1week)]:expiry:(never 1min 10min 1hour 24hour 1week 1month 1year)' \
        '--data-dir=[data directory (default microbin_data)]:directory:_files -/' \
        '(-n --no-file-upload)'{-n,--no-file-upload}'[disable file upload feature]' \
        '--custom-css=[custom CSS file URL]:url:' \
        '--hash-ids[hash pasta IDs (default sequential)]' \
        '--list-server[expose this server on the microbin public list]' \
        '--disable-telemetry[disable analytics telemetry]' \
        '--disable-update-checking[disable update-availability checks on startup]' \
        '--encryption-client-side=[allow client-side encryption (default true)]:bool:(true false)' \
        '--encryption-server-side=[allow server-side encryption (default true)]:bool:(true false)' \
        '--default-privacy=[default privacy mode]:mode:(public private unlisted)' \
        '--max-file-size-encrypted-mb=[max encrypted upload size in MB]:MB:' \
        '--max-file-size-unencrypted-mb=[max unencrypted upload size in MB]:MB:' \
        '--default-view=[default listing view (default gallery)]:view:(gallery list grid)'
}

_microbin "$@"
